descriptionHtml:
Do you like sports and minigames?

Play predicting on the results of the most competitive sports in the world and become an expert!
But not only this, you can also have fun and win coins by playing addictive minigames of all kinds!

Features:

-There are +30 minigames in our platform and different competitions every week with millions of coins in rewards!
-In sports, you can make your predictions in different markets as final result, double chance, Over/Under 2.5 goals. And more!
-You can make multiple or single bets in the events you want and the way you want.
-You can restart your funds in your account as many times as you want in the "Settings" section
-If you invite your friends to play Betsim you will receive a great reward!
Follow us on our social networks and participate in our weekly events to win more bycoins.

Play in more than 10 sports available from all the leagues and most important competitions in the world.
